==English==
===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/siːl/}}

===Etymology 1===
[[Image:Hydrurga leptonyx.JPG|thumb|a leopard seal (marine mammal)]]
From an inflectional form of Old English ''[[seolh]]''

====Noun====
{{en-noun-reg}}

# A type of [[pinniped]], a large marine fish-eating [[mammal]].
#: ''The '''seals''' in the harbor looked better than they smelled.''
[[Category:Mammals]]

